       <div class="layout">
        <div class="feature-story--item">
         <h2 class="title">
          Indiana University leads the largest state-based response to the addictions crisis
         </h2>
         <p class="show-for-medium">
          The nation is facing an unprecedented opioid addiction crisis. IU researchers are collaborating across industries to change the way addiction is treated and prevented.
         </p>
         <a class="button" href="/stories/features/fighting-addiction/index.html?&amp;ntm_source=news.iu.edu/index.html&amp;ntm_medium=web&amp;ntm_campaign=iu_news&amp;ntm_term=feature&amp;ntm_content=Indiana University leads the largest state-based response to the addictions crisis">
          Responding to addiction at IU
         </a>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
